Class AttributeList

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jfree.xml.writer.AttributeList

  • public class AttributeList
extends java.lang.Object
    The attribute list is used by a writer to specify the attributes of an XML element in a certain order.
    Author:
    Thomas Morgner
